# Voice Guide — Template

Replace this file with your own `voice.md`. This is the single most important customisation file.

Write it in first person, as a briefing to a ghostwriter. Include:

---

## Who you are

[Your name], [your role] at [your organisation]. Known for [what you're known for].

## Your audience

Primarily [describe audience — seniority, function, industry]. They come to you for [what value you provide].

## Your three content pillars

1. **[Pillar 1]**: [2–3 sentence description of what you cover]
2. **[Pillar 2]**: [2–3 sentence description]
3. **[Pillar 3]**: [2–3 sentence description]

## Your sentence rhythm

[Describe your style. Example: Short declarative sentences. No more than 20 words per sentence. Occasional single-sentence paragraphs for emphasis.]

Paste 2–3 examples from your past writing here so the AI can match your rhythm.

## Words and phrases you would never use

- leverage, synergy, game-changer, thought leader
- [add your own]

## What you want readers to feel after reading a post

[Example: Curious enough to question an assumption they held. Not lectured — challenged.]
